{{Infobox mine | name = Jacobs Ranch | image = | width = | caption = | pushpin_map = Wyoming | pushpin_label = Jacobs Ranch | pushpin_map_caption = Location in Wyoming | coordinates = {{coord|43|44|52|N|105|16|49|W|format=dms|display=inline,title}} | display = | place = | subdivision_type = [[U.S. state|State]] | state/province = [[Wyoming]] | country = United States | owner = [[Rio Tinto Energy America]] ([[Rio Tinto Group]]) | official website = | acquisition year = | stock_exchange = | stock_code = | products = [[Coal]] (38,100,000 tons per annum) | financial year = | amount = | opening year = | closing year = }}
'''Jacobs Ranch''' is a large [[open-pit mining|open-pit]] [[coal mine]] located 15 miles southeast of [[Wright, Wyoming]] in the coal-rich [[Powder River Basin]].<ref name="RTEA">{{cite web|url=http://www.rtea.com/pages/jacobsranch.aspx |title=Jacobs Ranch Mine |work=Rio Tinto Energy America website |publisher=Rio Tinto Group |accessdate=2009-04-21 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081211014330/http://www.rtea.com/pages/jacobsranch.aspx |archivedate=December 11, 2008 }}</ref> In 2007, the mine produced 38.1 million [[short ton]]s of coal, making it the fourth-largest coal mine by production in the United States.<ref name="EIA">{{cite web|url=http://www.eia.doe.gov/cneaf/coal/page/acr/table9.html|title=Major U.S. Coal Mines, 2007|date=September 2008|publisher=[[Energy Information Administration]] of the [[United States Department of Energy]]|accessdate=2009-04-14}}</ref>
==Information== Until 2009 the Jacobs Ranch mine was owned by [[Rio Tinto Energy America]], an American-based subsidiary of the international mining giant [[Rio Tinto Group]].<ref name="RTEA"/> In early 2009, Rio Tinto reached an agreement to sell the Jacobs Ranch mine to [[Arch Coal]] for $761 million.<ref name="Bloomberg-coal">{{cite web | last = Foley | first = Brett | last2 = Herlihy | first2 = Mark | title = Arch Coal to Buy U.S. Mine From Rio for $761 Million (Update 2) | publisher = [[Bloomberg.com]] | date = March 9, 2009 | url = https://www.bloomberg.com/apps/news?pid=20601085&sid=aQRIkg28LZxA&refer=europe | accessdate = March 12, 2009}}</ref>
