{{noref|date=April 2013}} The supposed [[Martian canal]]s were named, by [[Giovanni Schiaparelli|Schiaparelli]] and others, after real and legendary rivers of various places on Earth or the mythological underworld. Some of those names are listed below, with the regions that the canals were thought to connect.
