The '''Oceanium''' is a [[public aquarium]] that opened in 2001 in [[Diergaarde Blijdorp]], a [[zoo]] in [[Rotterdam]], [[Netherlands]].
The Oceanium lies in the expansion area of the zoo, which includes a new entrance and parking area, and was the biggest project to date for the zoo.<ref name=Rotterdamistop/> The area around the Oceanium is home to projects depicting [[the Americas]].

The Oceanium is also home to scientific research into the conservation of [[coral]].

